fields.description: When TRUE, allows device reset on installation failure. When false, reset is blocked. The default is false.
fields.name: AllowDeviceResetOnInstallFailure

fields.description: When TRUE, allows the user to continue using the device on installation failure. When false, blocks the user on installation failure. The default is false.
fields.name: AllowDeviceUseOnInstallFailure

fields.description: When TRUE, allows log collection on installation failure. When false, log collection is not allowed. The default is false.
fields.name: AllowLogCollectionOnInstallFailure

fields.description: When TRUE, ESP (Enrollment Status Page) installs all required apps targeted during technician phase and ignores any failures for non-blocking apps. When FALSE, ESP fails on any error during app install. The default is false.
fields.name: AllowNonBlockingAppInstallation

fields.description: When TRUE, blocks user from retrying the setup on installation failure. When false, user is allowed to retry. The default is false.
fields.name: BlockDeviceSetupRetryByUser

fields.description: The custom error message to show upon installation failure. Max length is 10000. example: 'Setup could not be completed. Please try again or contact your support person for help.'
fields.name: CustomErrorMessage

fields.description: When TRUE, disables showing installation progress for first user post enrollment. When false, enables showing progress. The default is false.
fields.name: DisableUserStatusTrackingAfterFirstUser

fields.description: The installation progress timeout in minutes. Default is 60 minutes.
fields.name: InstallProgressTimeoutInMinutes

fields.description: Allows quality updates installation during OOBE
fields.name: InstallQualityUpdates

fields.description: Selected applications to track the installation status. It is in the form of an array of GUIDs.
fields.name: SelectedMobileAppIds

fields.description: When TRUE, shows installation progress to user. When false, hides installation progress. The default is false.
fields.name: ShowInstallationProgress

fields.description: When TRUE, installation progress is tracked for only Autopilot enrollment scenarios. When false, other scenarios are tracked as well. The default is false.
fields.name: TrackInstallProgressForAutopilotOnly
